datasource.query:
SELECT
	'',
    IF (cloud='GCP', number, null) as GCP,
    IF (cloud='AWS', number, null) as AWS,
    IF (cloud='Azure', number, null) as Azure,
    IF (cloud='DigitalOcean', number, null) as DigitalOcean
FROM (
SELECT
	REGEXP_EXTRACT(labels, r'\|machine_type:(.*?)\|') AS machine_type,
	REGEXP_EXTRACT(labels, r'\|cloud:(.*?)\|') AS cloud,
	avg(value) AS number
FROM
	[{{ dataset_name }}.{{ table_name }}]
WHERE
	timestamp >= TIMESTAMP_TO_SEC(DATE_ADD(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), -3, 'MONTH')) AND
	product_name = 'PerfKitBenchmarker' AND
	test = 'aerospike' AND
	metric = 'max_throughput_for_completion_latency_under_1ms' 
GROUP BY
	machine_type,
	cloud
ORDER BY
  number ASC  
)
WHERE 
  machine_type = 'n1-standard-1' OR
  machine_type = 'm3.medium' OR
  machine_type = 'Small' OR
  machine_type = '2gb'
